<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَحْنِ الْقَوْلِ}</span> ... مَا يَبْدُو مِنْ كَلَامِهِمُ الَّذِي يَدُلُّ عَلَى مَقَاصِدِهِمْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَنَبْلُوَنَّكُمْ}</span> ... لَنَخْتَبِرَنَّكُمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَنَبْلُوَ أَخْبَارَكُمْ}</span> ... نَخْتَبِرَ أَقْوَالَكُمْ وَأَفْعَالَكُمْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَشَاقُّوا}</span> ... خَالَفُوهُ، وَحَارَبُوهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلَا تَهِنُوا}</span> ... لَا تَضْعُفُوا، وَتَجْبُنُوا عَنْ مُقَاتَلَةِ الكُفَّارِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السَّلْمِ}</span> ... الصُّلْحِ، وَالمُسَالَمَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَتِرَكُمْ أَعْمَالَكُمْ}</span> ... يَنْقُصَكُمْ ثَوَابَ أَعْمَالِكُمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٣٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَيُحْفِكُمْ}</span> ... يُلِحَّ عَلَيْكُمْ، وَيُجْهِدْكُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَضْغَانَكُمْ}</span> ... أَحْقَادَكُمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>